This is a shar archive for the paper:

	How to be Pessmistic:  Choquet Risk and Portfolio Optimization
		by  G.W. Bassett, R. Koenker and G Kordas

to be presented at the 4th L1 Neuchatel Meeting, August 2002.

There are several files 

	3 figures in postscript
	a bibtex file port.bib
	two style file for the bibliography.  

		The Sample document didn't specify a style so I went
		with my usual formatting.

	To make a ps file on most systems you would need to do something
	like the following:

		latex birk
		bibtex birk
		latex birk
		latex birk
		dvips birk

Please let me know if you have any questions.



